{"tid":1164336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂既50萬存款保障其實係咪港共泵水救火既前奏？","createTime":"2019-05-21T04:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T04:17:33.000Z","uid":190378,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c867cd36a24aeb30bd3651e5031258b2bcb98d01","tid":1164336,"uid":190378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"由早排開始，香港多左個銀行存款保障計劃而且仲要大費周章去賣廣告去宣傳同強調「最高保障50萬港紙」（包括外幣)，但呢樣野本來一直都無，而且仲要講到有咁安全得咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n講起「逃犯條例」我就突然間諗起呢個畫蛇添足既保障，到底兩者之間有無關係？定係一個早就諗好既前奏？<br />\n<br />\n今時今日好難相信呢個影子「政府」，你睇下山竹過左咁耐d樹都係早一兩個月先搞好哂，除左出賣香港人仲有d咩做得到？<br />\n<br />\n利伸:後知後覺"},{"pid":"476f3b4f0645d3a4f31d1f55c61b8f5cfe188be2","tid":1164336,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"講多無謂<br />\n撳哂出嚟換美金現鈔最實際"},{"pid":"edbdbd6ec5a2a95cca55881d105051d1a20e462c","tid":1164336,"uid":82310,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:06:48.000Z","msg":"2006年，香港根據《存款保障計劃條例》推出存款保障計劃（存保計劃），為存款人提供保障。假如存保計劃的成員銀行倒閉，無論個人或公司存戶，均可獲最高達50萬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thechinfamily.hk/web/sc/financial-products/personal-banking/deposit-protection-scheme.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thechinfamily.hk%2Fweb%2Fsc%2Ffinancial-products%2Fpersonal-banking%2Fdeposit-protection-scheme.html&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbZdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=f13d8760\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thechinfamily.hk/web/sc/financial-products/personal-banking/deposit-protection-scheme.html</a>"},{"pid":"689f1a3bbe0d71ec46c51f0e4e050759c2918e51","tid":1164336,"uid":230416,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"有咗十幾年喇喎，樓豬係新移民？"},{"pid":"0f6062af5127c587dc3951bbee2f0a4df82321d5","tid":1164336,"uid":74685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"坐咗幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419da1318b54a66e7e1dc39cbec